Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:42.43,song-op,,0,0,0,,The ball's shadow is growing tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:50.02,song-op,,0,0,0,,Don't be so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:54.11,song-op,,0,0,0,,Whenever we meet in the hallway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:58.45,song-op,,0,0,0,,we always quarreled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:06.67,song-op,,0,0,0,,Halfway through a kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:13.76,song-op,,0,0,0,,tears dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:21.10,song-op,,0,0,0,,Because I opened my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:27.90,song-op,,0,0,0,,and we understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Episode #23\NThe Secret is Revealed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.82,0:01:48.32,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Can I have an ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:48.82,Default,man,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:50.79,Default,man,0,0,0,,That's 50 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:52.71,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:57.43,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Hey, Tomomi! Aren't we supposed to share it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:01:58.65,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:01.97,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,If you can catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:05.01,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:07.30,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.91,0:02:13.68,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Oops. She found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:21.34,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:34.48,Default,kid,0,0,0,,I am Birdman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:37.05,Default,kid,0,0,0,,I'll get you, Squirrelman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:43.33,Default,kid,0,0,0,,Birdman, transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:48.38,Default,kid,0,0,0,,Meet your fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.16,Default,girl,0,0,0,,Do you like Alice too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:13.80,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Yeah, she reminds me of a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:19.30,Default,girl,0,0,0,,Rick says he doesn't get the story so he hates it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:20.35,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:24.14,Default,girl,0,0,0,,My big brother. He likes Birdman better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:25.78,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,So, you're looking after the store?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:26.30,Default,girl,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:39.92,Default,girl,0,0,0,,You like it? But I can't sell it because it's my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:08.87,Default,girl,0,0,0,,Rick! Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:10.86,Default,girl,0,0,0,,Somebody, help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:13.99,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:30.00,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Rick, Birdman doesn't scream. Hang on tight to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:37.14,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Senpai... senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:46.54,Default,kid,0,0,0,,He's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:47.46,Default,girl,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:05:00.16,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Senpai, how do I look in the costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:01.55,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,You look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:02.95,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:05.26,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,But you got the role all of a sudden, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:09.02,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,The girl who got the role was injured the day before, so here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.90,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Did you memorize the lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:15.34,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:17.59,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:18.98,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:20.59,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Then what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:21.99,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,The show's on today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.28,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Tomomi will help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:28.60,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,But I'll be fine. This is the last school test in jr. high.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:31.41,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Besides, you'll be watching. Better do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:43.50,announce,announcer,0,0,0,,Attention all cast of jr. secondary level play "Alice in Wonderland."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.66,Default,announcer,0,0,0,,There will be a rehearsal in the gym at ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:52.01,Default,announcer,0,0,0,,You are to be there ten minutes prior to the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:06:03.49,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,Why does a teacher in the senior secondary level have to play the Mad Hatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.96,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,But you fit right into the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:09.70,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,Now let us begin the rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:15.39,Default,student,0,0,0,,Alice, I'll read you a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:17.89,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,How wonderful, big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:20.84,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,But books without pictures are too boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:24.32,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,But books without pictures are too boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:27.87,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I want to know more about a dream-like land.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:31.73,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,I want to know more about a dream-like land.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:33.74,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:35.51,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,So that's what she meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:38.56,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,They're twins OK. They're synced so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:43.21,Default,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,Noda, you gonna leave me out there baking all those octopus balls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.30,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:50.02,Default,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,Is she Mikage-chan's twin sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:50.99,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:53.84,Default,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,That's right. It's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:55.18,Default,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,Cuuuteee~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:58.08,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,So she has a twin sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:07:00.31,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,Why are you staring at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:01.89,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:06.61,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,What is that? A white bunny?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:09.95,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,What is that? A white bunny?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:13.45,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,They look exactly alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:14.56,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:19.51,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Oops. That was "A white bunny is running in a great hurry."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:21.96,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,I wish you wouldn't alter the lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.13,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,If you want to help, do so accurately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.25,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:28.57,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,What's wrong with making small mistakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:33.49,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,It took me half a year to write this up! It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:36.13,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Gee, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:39.13,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,And I take it you aren't taking it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:40.76,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.92,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,Or don't you remember lines at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:47.32,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Not really. How should I remember it all in three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:52.03,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,Once you took the role, you had to do your best, regardless of the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:55.06,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,But she insisted I do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:56.98,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,That's an excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:59.25,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,If you're going to do the role, I'd expect you to do it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:02.01,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,Besides, Tomomi-chan's not a student of this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:04.99,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,Therefore, she's not involved in the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:07.96,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Alright! I'll do it by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:09.99,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,I won't ask for Tomomi's help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:12.44,Default,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,Damn Daijouji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:13.71,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,What's she going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:16.23,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:17.77,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:18.84,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Will you still help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:25.66,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,But that's too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:28.00,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Senpai's gonna be watching the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:31.74,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,I can't mess it up. See over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:37.22,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Nobody would notice if you do it in the PA booth. Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:40.99,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Anything for a love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:54.31,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:59.03,Default,announcer,0,0,0,,Yes? Oh you aren't Mikage-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:02.28,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I'm Tomomi. May I see the practice from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:03.34,Default,announcer,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:09.90,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,Let us resume the rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:12.40,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mikage, ready?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:14.68,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:16.19,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,From the beginning again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:18.66,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,{\i1}But books without pictures are too boring.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:21.36,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,But books without pictures are too boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:24.45,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to know more about a dream-like land.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:28.26,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,I want to know more about a dream-like land.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:30.52,Default,student,0,0,0,,Will Mikage be OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:31.23,Default,student,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.23,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,She'd start whining soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:38.95,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,How far will I fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.42,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,I must've fallen all the way to the other side of Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:44.75,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Where am I? Where will I be? Australia or New Zealand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:49.01,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where am I? Where will I be? Australia or New Zealand?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.76,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,What is so fun, did you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:56.55,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Yes, what is so fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:59.13,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:03.22,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,Can you imagine holding a tea party over and over?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:06.26,Default,bunnyguy,0,0,0,,No time to wash dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:10.53,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Is that why you have been playing musical chairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:12.73,Default,student,0,0,0,,She's got everything right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:14.92,Default,student,0,0,0,,She must've memorized them during the break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:17.66,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,She'd better. After all, she's the leading role.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:21.20,Default,Mika&guys,0,0,0,,Here's to the tea party by fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:22.40,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,What's going on?..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:27.76,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,I'm getting terrified of my own talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:34.09,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,Oh no. I must've drank too much tea. To the washroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:40.59,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,What's she doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:42.75,Default,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:49.15,Default,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,Tomomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:54.52,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,What is it? You want to date with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.50,Default,student,0,0,0,,There's no line like that, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.90,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I don't have time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:03.20,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,I don't have time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:05.21,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:07.04,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:10.72,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Mikage, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:14.42,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Mikage, what should I do?..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:19.54,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,Ma-Matsunaga-san, have you gone crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:23.88,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomomi, what are you doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.65,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry! I'll do something about it real quick!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:31.44,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,Something is wrong with Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:34.10,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,There might be something about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:38.84,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,There is said to be this special link between twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.03,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,What link?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:45.28,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,A telepathy. Very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:03.23,Default,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,Delicious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:06.65,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,{\i1}You must be Mr. Caterpillar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:09.28,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,You must be Mr. Caterpillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:17.32,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,I am not. I am Bokuen Hidari,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:19.74,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,the teacher of Japanese history for 45 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:23.24,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,Students, don't smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:27.08,Default,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,Tomomi-chan, if you're scared, you can hang onto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:34.62,Default,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:37.67,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Why are you grinning all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:41.17,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Why are you grinning all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:45.02,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,And what is wrong with your stomach? That is so hideous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:46.63,Default,catguy,0,0,0,,How is this then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:48.13,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:49.83,Default,student,0,0,0,,She's doing perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:51.40,Default,student,0,0,0,,She's a genius after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:54.76,Default,Daijouji,0,0,0,,So I have chosen the right girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:01.65,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Finally, it's over. Where's Yamagishi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:02.83,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,Tomomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.57,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Noda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.68,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,Aren't you bored?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:10.65,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,Don't worry about what Daijouji said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:14.11,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,No problem. But it looks so fun to be in a co-ed school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:16.49,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,It's got this vitality that I don't see in a girls school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:24.13,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,You know, Tomomi-chan, why don't you apply for this school next year?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.88,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,I think I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:30.24,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Where's Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:31.39,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Mikage-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:33.62,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Kurashige-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:36.41,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,So you had all the lines memorized after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:40.39,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Well... It's all thanks to Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:45.82,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Tomomi-kun was? You two are really close to each other, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:50.36,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Yes. It's so comforting to be with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:54.25,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,I think you could do well in track and field.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:55.36,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:57.20,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,I bet you're a fast runner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:59.74,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Then, I'll seriously go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:02.84,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,Yeah, do. It'll be fun. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:06.72,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,I'll go buy yakisoba. Our club's is real great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs20}Note: yakisoba = fried noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.77,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Same school as Mikage's, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.21,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,Tomomi Matsunaga-kun, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:16.23,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:20.40,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,I am Kageura, the science teacher of this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:23.34,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,There has been an alteration on the script of the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:27.97,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,We need to give the new script to Mikage-kun, but I can't find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:31.16,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,Will you come with me to get the script?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:44.95,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.98,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,They said I can have a half an hour break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.76,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Let's go eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:52.05,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.19,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,Tomomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:57.23,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.72,0:15:00.32,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,But you two really look alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:03.50,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,But I'm me, and Tomomi is Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:08.83,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,You're right, but to us, twins are very mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:10.51,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:15.50,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Enough to make me feel that you might have some wonderful secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:18.35,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:19.97,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,I must've got it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:23.32,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,Hey, Mikage! Seen Tomomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.15,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,I just saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:28.48,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,She was heading over to the school building with Kageura-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.04,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Where's the printing room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:32.13,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,Just a little ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:35.49,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,But we aren't going up to the roof, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.46,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,Come with me. We don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:40.62,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Mikage-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:42.44,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,Mikage, what's wrong with ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:44.87,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomomi, do you hear me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:47.71,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Sensei, aren't we at...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:58.33,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:15:58.93,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:01.88,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mikage, what's with this teacher?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:02.80,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:03.66,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the roof.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:09.14,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomomi, he's into psychic stuff. Just tell him you don't know anything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:17.52,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:19.74,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,I needed to ask you several questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:23.29,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,What were you doing over in the PA booth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:24.34,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:25.51,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:26.76,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:27.31,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.85,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,She really came!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:32.63,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:36.64,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,Before I answer that, how did you know where your sister is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:39.03,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Why? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:41.60,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,I'll tell you why.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:43.57,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,A telepathy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:46.27,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,No. Just an intuition!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:49.50,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,That is the most typical telepathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:51.98,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,Tomomi-chan, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:53.20,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,It's locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:58.01,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll keep it secret from your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.87,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,You are mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:04.42,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,What other powers can you use other than telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:07.01,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,I'd love to see you two teleport.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:09.74,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,How can we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:12.56,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,What's he doing up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:14.30,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Noda, gotta break down the door with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:15.93,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Would you unlock the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.67,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,The play is going to start soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:21.42,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,I don't care about the play anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:23.04,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,I want to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:30.61,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,How dare you break the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:31.81,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:50.72,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:52.56,Default,teacher,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:56.12,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:57.42,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Mikage-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:01.55,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Tomomi, hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:05.08,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,You're getting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:09.83,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Mikage-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:10.52,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,Tomomi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:19.18,Default,Kura&Noda,0,0,0,,Oh... they disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.13,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,We weren't dreaming, were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:35.92,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,You're shivering?..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:40.05,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... for not telling you all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:45.23,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,I thought you'd avoid me if I told you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:50.08,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,I didn't want you to avoid me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:54.84,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,What I said before was right, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:19:02.70,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,I don't know how to put it, but I feel that a wonderful thing just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:04.51,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:10.18,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,Awesome! You two are really neat! You just got me all excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:17.49,Default,announcer,0,0,0,,The play by jr. secondary level, "Alice in Wonderland"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:20.14,Default,announcer,0,0,0,,will start in a moment in the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.83,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Mikage-kun, you better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:25.92,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,The show won't start without Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:27.84,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Thank you, senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.84,0:19:29.21,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Noda-kun, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:30.33,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:40.39,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,So ESPers do exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:44.36,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Let's keep it secret. Just among the four of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:32.86,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Are you sure I can have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:35.61,Default,girl,0,0,0,,Sure. Will you give it to your friend in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:36.70,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:39.51,Default,kid,0,0,0,,Come back when you get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:44.04,Default,girl,0,0,0,,And is this friend your sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:48.04,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:59.78,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,That's weird. He should be on that plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:07.55,Default,stewardess,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting down in the lobby after I get your luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:08.42,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:19.40,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,Hey! Kurashige-senpai isn't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:24.61,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,He arrived already. I just sent Mikage in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:25.67,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.67,0:21:26.88,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Don't disturb them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:31.09,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:32.77,Default,Kurashige,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:35.05,Default,Mikage,0,0,0,,Isn't this Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:53.98,Default,preview,0,0,0,,Senpai, I'll visit you every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:55.08,Default,preview,0,0,0,,Mikage, you got a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:57.34,Default,preview,0,0,0,,There's this pretty woman in his hospital room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:21:58.28,Default,preview,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.59,0:22:00.04,Default,preview,0,0,0,,Next on Miracle Girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:02.03,Default,preview,0,0,0,,"What? Senpai's Lover?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.49,0:22:04.92,Default,preview,0,0,0,,We'll teleport to your heart tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:09.26,song-ed,,0,0,0,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:12.56,song-ed,,0,0,0,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:15.89,song-ed,,0,0,0,,Even if we had a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:19.10,song-ed,,0,0,0,,There has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:35.75,song-ed,,0,0,0,,There are days when kindness is so close
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:39.04,song-ed,,0,0,0,, that you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:52.55,song-ed,,0,0,0,,Even if we know it better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:58.98,song-ed,,0,0,0,,When we can't say "I'm sorry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.06,0:23:04.75,song-ed,,0,0,0,,we send out feelings through the little fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:15.70,song-ed,,0,0,0,,we want to be honest to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:21.13,song-ed,,0,0,0,,'Cause the sky deserves a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:24.17,song-ed,,0,0,0,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:27.63,song-ed,,0,0,0,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:30.72,song-ed,,0,0,0,,Two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:34.10,song-ed,,0,0,0,,are better than one of us.
